{"tid":491304,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"《籃球》勇士隊0：102遭完封 締造美國110年歷史","createTime":"2017-12-06T11:38:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T12:38:06.000Z","uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"68ff173fb3aa4503e852d72e5eb8655762f7808d","tid":491304,"uid":161311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T11:38:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sports.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2274926\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2274926&d=UZhO%2BqJXOpLBLF1A1KKHvF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=113338c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2274926&h=6b5eae8c\" target=\"_blank\">http://sports.ltn.com.tw/m/news/breakingnews/2274926</a><br />\n<br />\n美國出現百年來第20場完封籃球賽。（取自網路）<br />\n<br />\n〔體育中心／綜合報導〕布羅克高中女子籃球隊「勇士（Warriors）」上週遭蒙大拿紅鷹（Redhawks）以0：102完封，成為美國1907年以來第20場被完封的籃球賽，在網路上掀起話題。<br />\n<br />\n布羅克勇士隊總教練強森（Terrence Johnson）表示，他們原本有9至10名球員，未料隨著2017-18年賽季接近，他們因為各種原因失去球員，包括感冒，等到第一戰他們能用的球員只有5個人。<br />\n<br />\n「我們只有1名8年級生、1名來一年的新人、還有3名高一，其中1名高一是6年級以來首次打球，新人則是今年才真正開始打球。」強森無奈地說。<br />\n人手不足又稚嫩的勇士隊，最高球員只有170公分，卻對上有3名超過6呎（大約182公分）球員的紅鷹隊，全場被壓著猛打，比賽沒多久，勇士隊又接連因傷僅剩下3名球員在場上，半場結束0：59，最後以0：102慘敗。<br />\n<br />\n對於這場失控的比賽，紅鷹隊教練布雷克（Lance Brekke）賽後替對手球員感到難過，表示不希望再看到類似狀況發生；強森則說，女孩已盡全力要得分，因此不會對紅鷹隊有不滿的感覺。"},{"pid":"fa59d95ba223878191b2f9234a0d3e6223ffa6c6","tid":491304,"uid":146726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"依d仲叫比賽咩"},{"pid":"c3e91331faf6f08bd797f906301ebc262f27e31e","tid":491304,"uid":59536,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依d仲叫比賽咩</blockquote><br />\n#metoo"},{"pid":"c50859a335c325cc1956cf51c32060a8658398af","tid":491304,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T11:54:26.000Z","msg":"宇宙湧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5c0d02d88c28edd1c6ad15a7f469b41a44685a8","tid":491304,"uid":29130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T11:56:57.000Z","msg":"#metoo"},{"pid":"ba3a068cfd40143a1832df34fe5ab58e9c302473","tid":491304,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T11:57:30.000Z","msg":"Let go hawks"},{"pid":"d4b6b41fc1d6be6d8fbcdcc6782d9c780129daf4","tid":491304,"uid":140450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:34:12.000Z","msg":"[quoteiu]依d仲叫比賽咩[/quote]<br />\n<blockquote>引用</blockquote><blockquote>b</blockquote>k"},{"pid":"b805a6d6b3b2281a2074c51e61262baf26a611e6","tid":491304,"uid":55193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"唔夠5個都可以繼續打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}